## ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Files created by development tools
/.idea/
*.iml
**/*.rs~
**/*.md~

## ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Files created by cargo (build, fmt, make, etc.)
/.cargo
/target
/docs
/bin
Cargo.lock
**/*.rs.bk

## ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Files required for CI integration (Travis)
/ci
frontend/node_modules/
frontend/dist/

## ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# sqlite 数据库文件(运行时产生,非源码)
*.sqlite
*.sqlite-shm
*.sqlite-wal
frontend/package-lock.json

# 任意插件的 UI 目录:node_modules / 构建产物 / 包锁 / vite/tsc 缓存
# 不绑定具体插件名,新增插件到 plugins/<name>/ 也会自动适用
**/plugins/*/ui/node_modules/
**/plugins/*/ui/dist/
**/plugins/*/ui/.vite/
**/plugins/*/ui/*.tsbuildinfo
**/plugins/*/ui/package-lock.json
**/plugins/*/release/

## ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Plugin UI legacy compiled output (kept during migration; remove after first clean build)
**/plugins/*/ui/panel.js
.playwright-cli/
/plugins/afp_plugin/release/libafp_plugin.dylib
/plugins/reuters_plugin/release/libreuters_plugin.dylib
